title: Harvey and Murphy lead Mets over Cubs 4-2 in NLCS opener
text:
> Sports Harvey and Murphy lead Mets over Cubs 4-2 in NLCS opener New York Mets' Travis d'Arnaud is congratulated in the dugout after hitting a home run during the sixth inning of Game 1 of the National League baseball championship series against the Chicago Cubs Saturday, Oct. 17, 2015, in New York.
